biography: Joakim is a golfer known for his calm demeanor on the course. While his home club remains a mystery, his presence is always felt at any event he attends.

Despite having participated in the Hector Trophée on one occasion, Joakim is yet to clinch the coveted Hector Trophée or the Victor Trophy. Sources close to Joakim say that he is very eager to have another shot at the title soon.
Although Joakim will not be participating in Hector Trophée 2025, fans should not give up hope, as last-minute changes to the field are always possible.
